source.name: LEHD Origin-Destination Employment Statistics (LODES)
source.description: LODES Data provides detailed spatial distributions of workers' employment and residential locations and the relation between the two at the Census Block level. LODES also provides characteristic detail on age, earnings, industry distributions, and local workforce indicators.
